title: Number of New Firms Established for Germany
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1908-1925 (2)--Original Data, 1925-1938. Figures Include Data From Business Establishments Of--(1)--Aktiengesellschaften (2)--Gesellschaften Mit Beschrankten Haftung (3)--Genossenschaften (4)--Kommanditgesellschaften (5)--Offene Handelsgesellschaften (6)--Einzelfirmen. Data Include Changes Of Gesellschaften Mit Beschrankten Haftung Into Einzelfirmen, Offene Handelsgesellschaften And Kommanditgesellschaften. Also Vice-Versa (See Description In Source). Data Were Checked With The Statistical Jahrbuch. Saarland Included In Data From March 1935-December 1938. Source: Statistiches Reichsamt, Wirtschaft Und Statistik

This NBER data series m10031b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 10 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter10.html.
